title: Banjaran
subTitle: The universe offers a Banjara tribe leader's daughter an opportunity to turn her doomed love story into a happily-ever-after with her soulmate.

title: Ram Avtar
subTitle: Childhood friends Ram and Avtar face a love triangle when Ram falls for Sangeeta, whom Avtar also loves. Ram sacrifices his love for Avtar, but their enemy Gundappaswami threatens to expose the truth.

title: Waqt Ki Awaz
subTitle: A rich girl runs away from home and settles down with a truck driver. However, her dream life is shattered when she learns that her new lover has been accused of murder.

title: Do Chor
subTitle: Tony, a burglar, comes under the radar of suspicion when a series of mysterious thefts bewilder the police. Soon enough, he tries to redeem his honour by going after the real criminal.

title: Gair Kaanooni
subTitle: Police Inspector Kapil Khanna realises that his baby boy has been switched with a girl child by the hospital and files a lawsuit against the owner, Robert Decosta while trying to find his missing son.

title: Deewaar: Let's Bring Our Heroes Home
subTitle: Haunted by the past, Vijay turns to crime, while Ravi, his younger brother, becomes an honest police officer. Fate pits them against each other when Ravi is sent to nab Vijay.

title: Gharana
subTitle: Prem Mehra loses everything after one of his employees joins hands with his rapacious rival and the two plot against him. Later, his sons work together to retrieve their family's lost wealth.

title: Global Baba
subTitle: Pehlwaan, a criminal, narrowly escapes a police encounter and uses a holy man's guise to hide. Though he soon amasses a large number of followers, he continues to carry out his illegal activities.

title: Mera Damad
subTitle: Jai's father asks him to meet Sunita before getting married to her. However, complications arise when Jai falls in love with Kimi, while on his way to Sunita's village.

title: Shool
subTitle: Inspector Samar is transferred to Motihari in Bihar, India, due to his honesty. He soon earns the wrath of a corrupt politician, Bachchu Yadav, who gradually becomes a threat to him and his family.

title: Bazaar
subTitle: Najma is in love with Akhtar but cannot marry him until he is financially stable. An elderly Shakir promises to help Akhtar set up his business in exchange for Najma finding a suitable bride for him.

title: Bazaar
subTitle: Najma is in love with Akhtar but cannot marry him until he is financially stable. An elderly Shakir promises to help Akhtar set up his business in exchange for Najma finding a suitable bride for him.

title: Lorie
subTitle: Geeta is expecting a baby but tragedy strikes and she loses her child. When she finds a little boy, she adopts him as her own but the boy's family accuses her of kidnapping.

title: Accident on Hill Road
subTitle: Sonam's night of celebration turns into a disaster when her car hits an innocent man. Afraid of being punished for the crime, she decides to hide him but invites trouble in turn.

title: Aan Baan
subTitle: Raja Bahadur indulges in various unlawful activities and is always saved by his brother, Suraj. When he decides to marry Rekha, Suraj, who is also in love with her, falls into a dilemma.

title: Neel Kamal
subTitle: Sita's sleepwalking turns out to be a cause of concern to her husband and family. When they investigate, they realize that her current behaviour is linked to her previous life.

title: Dil Kya Kare
subTitle: The parents of an adopted child face issues of love, betrayal and custody when their daughter's birth mother arrives.

title: Prem Kahani
subTitle: Rajesh, an apolitical poet, is in love with Kamini and leads a peaceful life. However, when his brother is killed by the British government, he decides to become a revolutionary and joins the freedom struggle.

title: Ek Chitthi Pyar Bhari
subTitle: A doctor puts out a job posting to recruit a nurse for his clinics in rural India. Unaware of a candidate's dark past, he hires her and eventually falls in love with her.

title: Sherni
subTitle: Durga, a simple village girl, watches her entire family die at the hands of Thakur. Soon, she picks up the gun and chooses a criminal lifestyle to avenge the death of her loved ones.

title: Ek Rishtaa: The Bond of Love
subTitle: Amid the ideological differences with his father Vijay, Ajay steps up to protect his family from Rajesh's, his brother-in-law's, evil intentions.

title: Jeans
subTitle: Madhumita and Vishwanathan fall in love with each other but his father disapproves of the relationship as he wants his twin sons to marry two identical twins.

title: Jeans
subTitle: Madhumita and Vishwanathan fall in love with each other but his father disapproves of the relationship as he wants his twin sons to marry two identical twins.

title: Do Premee
subTitle: Lovers Payal and Chetan elope as their families disapprove of their relationship. They start a new life working for Geeta, unaware of her true nature and affiliations.

title: Karamdaata
subTitle: Pinky, the granddaughter of a wealthy industrialist, runs away and marries a taxi driver. However, the businessman holds Pinky's lover responsible and gets him arrested.

title: Raja Saab
subTitle: Upon Prince Pratap's insistence, Rajoo impersonates him in front of Princess Poonam. But the imitation lands him in trouble when she starts falling for Rajoo, unaware of his poor background.

title: Rajjo
subTitle: A young man falls for a woman from the red-light district, but their love faces opposition and threat from powerful figures.

title: Dil Ka Rishta
subTitle: Jai, a wealthy businessman in love with Tia, accidentally kills her husband in a car crash. After the accident Tia loses her memory and falls for Jai, who struggles with guilt.

title: Ujala Hi Ujala
subTitle: Anuradha's stepmother forces her to consume alcohol and she becomes an addict. After her father's death, she takes over the business and falls in love with Vikram, but her happiness is short-lived.

title: Bumm Bumm Bole
subTitle: An idealist elder brother lands in a dilemma after he misplaces his little sister's shoes. Unable to afford a new pair, the siblings agree to share the shoes, leading to several escapades.

title: Officer Arjun Singh IPS
subTitle: Arjun Pratap Singh, an IPS officer, strives to overcome multiple challenges and embarks on a mission to restore peace in society.

title: Aflatoon
subTitle: Raja, a good-for-nothing fortune hunter, sets his sights on the daughter of a wealthy businessman. Before long, love takes over and brings about a twist in the tale.

title: Phullu
subTitle: Phullu's mother decides to marry him off to make him more mature. Things take an unexpected turn when he learns about menstruation after marriage.
